              <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Book early during peak season (May-June, September-October)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Carry your own sleeping bag for hygiene at high altitude camps</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>All our packages include accommodation - we handle bookings for you</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-600 text-white">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
        We Handle All Accommodation Bookings
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg opacity-90 mb-6 md:mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        When you book with us, we arrange all accommodations throughout your journey
      </p>
      <a href="/packages" class="btn-secondary text-base md:text-lg px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-4">
        View Packages
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

